      "content": {
        "type": "intro",
        "title": "The Architect of Autonomy",
        "subtitle": "The guiding storyline of my life",
        "hook_text": "Most people work harder. I decided to build systems that work for me."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "topic_001",
      "type": "topic",
      "duration_sec": 14,
      "start_time_sec": 5,
      "content": {
        "type": "topic",
        "heading": "The Blueprint Phase",
        "body_text": "I didn't start with answers \u2014 I started with obsession. Every video I made was me figuring it out in public, building a map no one had handed me.",
        "bullet_points": [
          "Learning through doing",
          "Documenting the process",
          "Building before the blueprint existed"
        ],
        "animation_style": "slide"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "topic_002",
      "type": "topic",
      "duration_sec": 14,
      "start_time_sec": 19,
      "content": {
        "type": "topic",
        "heading": "Systems Over Hustle",
        "body_text": "The most important shift wasn't a tactic \u2014 it was a philosophy. Discipline isn't grind culture. It's the architecture of a life you designed.",
        "bullet_points": [
          "AI systems that compound",
          "Honesty over hype",
          "Leverage through architecture"
        ],
        "animation_style": "slide"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "topic_003",
      "type": "topic",
      "duration_sec": 14,
      "start_time_sec": 33,
      "content": {
        "type": "topic",
        "heading": "The Alignment Gap",
        "body_text": "62% aligned with my own vision. That gap isn't failure \u2014 it's the fuel. The distance between who I am and who I'm becoming is where the work lives.",
        "bullet_points": [
          "Gap as direction, not deficit",
          "Inspiration vs. execution",
          "The proof-of-concept moment"
        ],
        "animation_style": "slide"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "topic_004",
      "type": "topic",
      "duration_sec": 14,
      "start_time_sec": 47,
      "content": {
        "type": "topic",
        "heading": "Content Superpower",
        "body_text": "I don't teach expertise. I perform the process of becoming one. That's what makes the work real \u2014 you're watching it happen, not hearing about it after.",
        "bullet_points": [
          "Performing the process publicly",
          "Radical transparency",
          "Building in real time"
        ],
        "animation_style": "slide"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "topic_005",
      "type": "topic",
      "duration_sec": 14,
      "start_time_sec": 61,
      "content": {
        "type": "topic",
        "heading": "The North Star",
        "body_text": "One person. AI systems. Uncompromising discipline. A fully autonomous business \u2014 built in public, documented in detail, so others can see it's possible.",
        "bullet_points": [
          "Proof that one person is enough",
          "AI as force multiplier",
          "Autonomy as the ultimate goal"
        ],
        "animation_style": "slide"
      }
    },
